
    <html xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" 
          xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word" 
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40">
    <head>
        <title>Project Planning Phase - Backlog, Sprints & Metrics</title>
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #2d2724;
                background-color: #faf6eb;
                margin: 20px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                color: #c05c46;
                border-bottom: 2px solid #2d2724;
                padding-bottom: 5px;
            }
            h2, h3, h4 {
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                color: #2d2724;
            }
            table {
                width: 100%;
                border-collapse: collapse;
                margin: 20px 0;
            }
            th, td {
                border: 2px solid #2d2724;
                padding: 10px;
                text-align: left;
            }
            th {
                background-color: #dda15e;
                color: #2d2724;
                font-weight: bold;
            }
            .meta-table {
                width: 50%;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }
            .meta-table th {
                background-color: #2d2724;
                color: #faf6eb;
            }
            .highlight {
                background-color: #faf6eb;
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                padding: 2px 5px;
                border: 1px solid #2d2724;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Project Planning Phase - Backlog, Sprints & Metrics</h1>
        <table class="meta-table">
            <tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Value</th></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Date</b></td><td>11 July 2026</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Team ID</b></td><td>TEAM-MERN-03</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Project Name</b></td><td>ShopEZ - Vintage Sepia Neubrutalist E-Commerce Platform</td></tr>
        </table>
        
    <h2>Product Backlog & Sprint Schedule</h2>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>Sprint</th>
            <th>Epic / Module</th>
            <th>User Story ID</th>
            <th>User Story / Task</th>
            <th>Story Points</th>
            <th>Priority</th>
            <th>Team Member</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Sprint-1</td>
            <td>Aesthetics</td>
            <td>USN-01</td>
            <td>As a user, I can view the catalog with a cozy warm vintage sepia layout.</td>
            <td>3</td>
            <td>High</td>
            <td>Design Lead</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Sprint-1</td>
            <td>Authentication</td>
            <td>USN-02</td>
            <td>As a buyer/seller, I can register or log in with secure guards.</td>
            <td>2</td>
            <td>High</td>
            <td>Backend Dev</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Sprint-2</td>
            <td>Checkout</td>
            <td>USN-03</td>
            <td>As a buyer, I can fill in shipping details and pay with a credit card.</td>
            <td>4</td>
            <td>High</td>
            <td>Frontend Dev</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Sprint-2</td>
            <td>Invoice</td>
            <td>USN-04</td>
            <td>As a buyer, I can view a print-friendly invoice page that hides navigation.</td>
            <td>2</td>
            <td>Medium</td>
            <td>Frontend Dev</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Sprint-3</td>
            <td>Dashboard</td>
            <td>USN-05</td>
            <td>As a seller, I can monitor store KPIs and view low-stock alerts.</td>
            <td>3</td>
            <td>High</td>
            <td>Fullstack Dev</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Sprint-4</td>
            <td>Resiliency</td>
            <td>USN-06</td>
            <td>As a user, if my token is deleted, I am logged out rather than showing errors.</td>
            <td>2</td>
            <td>High</td>
            <td>Backend Dev</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Project Tracker & Iteration Durations</h2>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>Sprint</th>
            <th>Total Story Points</th>
            <th>Duration</th>
            <th>Sprint Start Date</th>
            <th>Sprint End Date</th>
            <th>Completed Points</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Sprint-1</td>
            <td>18</td>
            <td>6 Days</td>
            <td>01 October 2026</td>
            <td>07 October 2026</td>
            <td>18</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Sprint-2</td>
            <td>20</td>
            <td>6 Days</td>
            <td>08 October 2026</td>
            <td>14 October 2026</td>
            <td>20</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Sprint-3</td>
            <td>15</td>
            <td>6 Days</td>
            <td>15 October 2026</td>
            <td>21 October 2026</td>
            <td>15</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <h3>Velocity and Burndown Estimation</h3>
    <p><b>Team Average Velocity:</b> 18 Story Points per sprint (6 days) &rarr; <b>3 Story Points per day</b>.</p>
    
